Class ConstIndexedList<Type>

java.lang.Object
  net.varkhan.base.containers.list.ConstIndexedList<Type>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable, Container<Type>, Indexable, Indexed<Type>, IndexedCollection<Type>, IndexedContainer<Type>, IndexedVisitable<Type>, IndexedList<Type>, Visitable<Type>
public class ConstIndexedList<Type>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IndexedList<Type>, java.io.Externalizable, java.lang.Cloneable

Constant-valued IndexedList.

An immutable IndexedList that returns a constant, predefined value for every index.
